<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pregnancy Calculators Hub | BloomCycle</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #e83f8e;
            --primary-light: #ff8fab;
            --primary-lighter: #ffc2d1;
            --secondary: #9c4668;
            --light: #fff9fb;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --text: #3a2e37;
            --bloom: linear-gradient(135deg, #e83f8e, #ff8fab);
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --shadow-hover: 0 15px 35px rgba(232, 63, 142, 0.15);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            background: var(--white);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--bloom);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .nav-logo i {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
            background-color: var(--primary-lighter);
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: var(--bloom);
            color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="100" height="100" opacity="0.1"><path fill="white" d="M30,30 Q50,10 70,30 T90,50 T70,70 T50,90 T30,70 T10,50 T30,30 Z"/></svg>');
            background-size: 200px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .calculators-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .calculator-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-lighter);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .calculator-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--bloom);
        }

        .calculator-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
        }

        .calculator-icon {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: var(--primary-lighter);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(232, 63, 142, 0.2);
        }

        .calculator-card h2 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            min-height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .calculator-card p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .calculator-features {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .calculator-features h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .calculator-features h3 i {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .calculator-features ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .calculator-features li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .calculator-features li:before {
            content: "✓";
            color: var(--primary);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--bloom);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(232, 63, 142, 0.3);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(232, 63, 142, 0.4);
        }

        .info-section {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-lighter);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .info-section::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--bloom);
        }

        .info-section h2 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary-lighter);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .info-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: var(--primary-lighter);
        }

        .info-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin: 15px 0 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .info-icon {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: var(--primary-lighter);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(232, 63, 142, 0.2);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--primary-lighter);
        }

        .heart {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        @media (max-width: 1200px) {
            .calculators-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 30px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .calculators-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 25px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .nav-links {
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .calculator-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .calculator-card h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                min-height: auto;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .calculators-grid {
                gap: 20px;
            }
            
            .calculator-card {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .calculator-icon {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <i class="fas fa-venus"></i>
                BloomCycle
            </div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/calculators"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Calculators</a>
                <a href="/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> My Account</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Pregnancy Calculators</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Essential tools to track your pregnancy journey with accuracy and care</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="intro">
            <p>Our collection of pregnancy calculators helps you understand and track important milestones during your pregnancy. Each tool is designed with medical accuracy and ease of use in mind, all within the trusted BloomCycle environment.</p>
        </section>

