                <div class="calculator-features">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Key Features:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Calculate hCG doubling time between two tests</li>
                        <li>Understand what your results mean</li>
                        <li>Track early pregnancy progression</li>
                        <li>Medical interpretation of results</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <a href="/hcg" class="btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Use hCG Calculator
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Implantation Calculator Card -->
            <div class="calculator-card">
                <div class="calculator-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrows-alt-h"></i>
                </div>
                <h2>Implantation Calculator</h2>
                <p>Determine when implantation might occur based on your cycle to understand early pregnancy timing.</p>
                
                <div class="calculator-features">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Key Features:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Calculate based on ovulation or last period</li>
                        <li>Account for different cycle lengths</li>
                        <li>Identify implantation window</li>
                        <li>Learn about implantation signs</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <a href="/implantations" class="btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Use Implantation Calculator
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Due Date Calculator Card -->
            <div class="calculator-card">
                <div class="calculator-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                </div>
                <h2>Pregnancy Due Date Calculator</h2>
                <p>Calculate your estimated due date and track your pregnancy progress through all trimesters.</p>
                
                <div class="calculator-features">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Key Features:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Multiple calculation methods</li>
                        <li>Trimester breakdown</li>
                        <li>Pregnancy progress tracking</li>
                        <li>IVF and ultrasound options</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <a href="/duedate" class="btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Use Due Date Calculator
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- IVF Due Date Calculator Card -->
            <div class="calculator-card">
                <div class="calculator-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-dna"></i>
                </div>
                <h2>IVF Due Date Calculator</h2>
                <p>Specialized calculator for IVF pregnancies with accurate dating for different transfer types.</p>
                
                <div class="calculator-features">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Key Features:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>3-day and 5-day embryo transfers</li>
                        <li>Frozen embryo transfer options</li>
                        <li>IVF-specific milestone tracking</li>
                        <li>Specialized IVF information</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <a href="/ivf" class="btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Use IVF Calculator
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>Understanding Your Pregnancy Journey</h2>
            <p>Pregnancy is an incredible journey with many milestones. Our calculators help you navigate this special time by providing accurate information when you need it most, all within the trusted BloomCycle environment.</p>
            
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Medical Accuracy</h3>
                    <p>All calculators are based on established medical principles and formulas used by healthcare professionals.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Designed for You</h3>
                    <p>Created with the needs of expecting parents in mind - simple, clear, and supportive.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Easy to Use</h3>
                    <p>Intuitive interfaces that work perfectly on all devices - desktop, tablet, or mobile.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Educational Resources</h3>
                    <p>Each calculator includes helpful information to understand your results in context.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>Disclaimer: These tools are for educational purposes only. Always consult with your healthcare provider for medical advice.</p>
            <p>Made with <span class="heart">♥</span> for all expecting parents | BloomCycle</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
